    "spell_type": "focus",
    "rank": 1,
    "text": "You attempt to calm the target by uttering soothing words in a calm and even tone. The target gains a +1 status bonus to Will saving throws. This bonus increases to +2 against emotion effects.  \n  \n In addition, when you Cast this Spell, you can attempt to counteract one emotion effect on the target.",
